#, no-c-format
msgid "&FTP;"
msgstr "FTP"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&FTP;, or File Transfer Protocol, is one of the the earliest, and still "
#| "perhaps the best, way of transferring files between computers over the "
#| "Internet."
msgid ""
"&FTP;, or File Transfer Protocol, is one of the earliest, and still perhaps "
"the best, way of transferring files between computers over the Internet."
msgstr ""
"FTP бһ¬ бһ–бһ·бһ’бһёбһҖбһ¶бһҡвҖӢбһ”бһүбҹ’бһҮбһјбһ“вҖӢвҖӢбһҜбһҖбһҹбһ¶бһҡ бһӮбһәбһҮбһ¶вҖӢбһ–бһ·бһ’бһёбһҖбһ¶бһҡвҖӢбһҳбһ»бһ“вҖӢбһӮбҹҒвҖӢбһҳбһҪбһҷ бһ бһҫбһҷбһ“бҹ…бһҸбҹӮвҖӢбһҳбһ¶бһ“бһӣбһҖбҹ’бһҒбһҺбҹҲвҖӢбһӣбҹ’бһўбһ”бҹҶбһ•бһ»бһҸвҖӢбһҖбҹ’бһ“бһ»бһ„бһҖбһ¶бһҡвҖӢбһ”бһүбҹ’бһ…бһјбһ“вҖӢбһҜбһҖбһҹбһ¶бһҡвҖӢвҖӢбһ–бһёвҖӢбһҖбһ»бҹҶбһ–бҹ’бһҷбһјбһ‘бҹҗбһҡвҖӢ"
"бһҳбһҪбһҷвҖӢбһ‘бҹ…вҖӢбһҳбһҪбһҷвҖӢвҖӢбһҸбһ¶бһҳвҖӢбһўбҹҠбһёбһ“бһ’бһәбһҺбһ·бһҸВ бҹ”"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1484
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "With &FTP; you can see files and folders on the distant computer just as "
#| "if they were on your own system, download them onto your computer using "
#| "&konqueror;'s normal <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and "
#| "<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> or Drag n' Drop methods and, if allowed, "
#| "upload files from your machine to the other computer's filesystem. To try "
#| "it, type the &URL;"
msgid ""
"With &FTP; you can see files and folders on the distant computer just as if "
"they were on your own system, download them onto your computer using "
"&konqueror;вҖҷs normal <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> or DragвҖҷn Drop methods and, if allowed, upload files from your "
"machine to the other computerвҖҷs filesystem. To try it, type the &URL;"
msgstr ""
